description.p:
In specific embodiments, the machining step includes the successive operations of:
positioning the cutting tool so that its axis of rotation is the same as the axis of rotation of the escapement wheel ébauche;
guiding the cutting tool in translation towards the escapement wheel ébauche according to a direction coaxial to the axis of rotation of the escapement wheel ébauche, and blanking a part of the end of each tooth of the escapement wheel ébauche so as to generate a reduced end portion, in a single cutting operation;
removing the tool.

The machining step is advantageously carried out by milling, and it includes the successive operations of:
positioning the cutting tool 20 so that its axis of rotation is the same as the axis of rotation of the escapement wheel ébauche;
guiding the cutting tool 20 in translation towards the escapement wheel ébauche according to a direction coaxial to the axis of rotation of the escapement wheel ébauche, and blanking a part of the end of each tooth 14 of the escapement wheel ébauche so as to reduce the thickness of said part, in a single cutting operation; this operation allows to obtain the reduced end portions of each tooth 14;
removing the cutting tool 20.
